prodNameC: 常盈類胰島素生長因子結合蛋白-3
ingredientsDesc:
IGFBP-3 Standard A/Sample Diluent:
One bottle, 55 mL, labeled A, containing 0 ng/mL IGFBP-3 in a protein-based (BSA) buffer with sodium azide as a preservative. 
IGFBP-3 Standards: 
Five vials, labeled B-F, containing concentrations of approximately 2.0, 5.0, 20.0, 50.0, 100.0 ng/mL of
IGFBP-3 in a protein-based (BSA) buffer.  
Anti-IGFBP-3 [I-125] Reagent:  
One bottle, 22 mL, containing <10 μCi (370 kBq) of [I-125]-labeled goat Anti-IGFBP-3 polyclonal antibody in
a protein-based (BSA) buffer with sodium azide as a preservative.

Anti-IGFBP-3-Coated Tubes: 
One hundred (100) plastic tubes with goat anti-IGFBP-3 polyclonal immunoglobulin immobilized to the inside
wall of each tube. 
IGFBP-3 Controls:
Two vials, Levels I and II, containing low and high levels of IGFBP-3 in a protein-based (BSA) buffer with
sodium azide as a preservative.
